ml.alternet.security.auth.formats

Class CryptFormatBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • ml.alternet.security.auth.formats.CryptFormatBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CryptFormat, DiscoverableCryptFormat
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ModularCryptFormat

    public abstract class CryptFormatBase
extends Object
implements CryptFormat, DiscoverableCryptFormat
    A crypt format based on enum values. First, the hasher builder is looked up within the built-in hashers available with getEnumValues() ; if not found, the scheme is extracted with parseScheme(Scanner) and looked up with the discovery service.
    Author:
    Philippe Poulard
